You can create up to 10 views per dashboard, including your own default view. All your saved views are listed in the view menu.
To create a view, open the dashboard in view mode, make your selections, and click Save View.

Saved views include all selections made on the current page in various widgets.
When you change a selection while viewing a dashboard or view, an asterisk appears next to the view name. You can save the current selections as a new view or overwrite an existing one.

To remove your changes to a dashboard or view, click . To set your default view or delete a view, click Manage Views.
title: Save Custom Views of Dashboards
